data.description: This home offers an inviting entry courtyard, OWNED SOLAR, newer HVAC system, newly painted interior with neutral shade, open concept, vaulted ceilings, lighted built in media center, , fireplace, lots of cabinets in kitchen for storage, breakfast island, pantry closet, laptop workstation, 3 walk in closets, bay windows throughout, jetted walk-in tub, a delightful multi-functional Arizona room for entertaining or cozying up in your favorite chair, an expansive backyard with pergola covered patio, built in seating island, firepit w wall seating, a soothing rock water feature, citrus trees and an opportunity to add a pool and/or casita.  The extended garage can accommodate 2 standard vehicles and 2 golf carts.  This home is Move-In-.Ready -Oasis pool nearby.  Don't pass up the chance to enrich your lifestyle in the award-winning resort style community of PebbleCreek!
